s]]''\n| 2018-19\n| Lance\n| 14 episodes\n|\n|-\n| scope=\"row\" | ''[[Neighbours]]''\n| 2020\n| Himself\n|\n|\n|}\n\n==Awards==\n{| class=\"wikitable plainrowheaders sortable\"\n|+ Awards\n|-\n! scope=\"col\" | Award\n! scope=\"col\" | Award category\n! scope=\"col\" | Year\n! scope=\"col\" | Result\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | [[Time Out (company)|Time Out]]\n| Best Stand-Up\n| 2006\n| Won<ref>[http://www.timeout.com/features/liveawards/winners.php?cat=comedy 20th Time Out Live Awards Winners \u2013 Comedy] by [[Time Out (company)|Time Out]] {{webarchive |url=https://web.archive.org/web/20060821033845/http://www.timeout.com/features/liveawards/winners.php?cat=comedy |date=21 August 2006 }}</ref>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | [[Loaded (magazine)|Loaded Laftas]]\n| Best Stand-Up\n| 2006\n| Won<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.loaded.co.uk/laftas |title=Loaded Laftas |website=Loaded.co.uk |date=27 May 2010 |accessdate=31 May 2010 |url-status=dead |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100603155700/http://www.loaded.co.uk/laftas |archivedate=3 June 2010 }}</ref>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | [[British Comedy Awards]]\n| Best Newcomer\n| 2006\n| Won<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.britishcomedyawards.com/past-winners/2006.aspx | title=Past Winners 2006 | website=Britishcomedyawards.com | accessdate=6 September 2013}}</ref>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | [[Broadcasting Press Guild|33rd Annual Television and Radio Awards]]\n| Best Television Performer in a Non-Acting Role\n| 2007\n| Won<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.broadcastingpressguild.org/ |title=Broadcasting Press Guild |publisher=Broadcasting Press Guild |accessdate=31 May 2010}}</ref>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | British Comedy Awards\n| Best Live Stand-Up\n| 2008\n| Won<ref>{{cite news|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/entertainment/7769652.stm |title=Brand wins British Comedy Award |work=BBC News |date=7 December 2008 |accessdate=31 May 2010}}</ref>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | Variety's Power of Comedy Award\n| \n| 2010\n| Won<ref>{{cite news |url=http: